org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.nodemanager.amrmproxy

接口 AMRMProxyApplicationContext

  • 所有已知实现类:
    AMRMProxyApplicationContextImpl

    public interface AMRMProxyApplicationContext
    Interface that can be used by the intercepter plugins to get the information about one application.
